{"word":"G4937 - συντρίβω - syntríbō - soon-tree'-bo - Break","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συντρίβω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>syntríbō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>soon-tree'-bo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Break"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நெரி, தகர், உடை, நருங்கு, கசக்கு, முறி, நசுக்கு, நொறுக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to break, to break in pieces, shiver"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5147 - τρίβος - tríbos - tree'-bos/5147\">G5147</a>; to <i>crush completely</i>, that is, to <i>shatter</i> (literally or figuratively): - break (in pieces), broken to shivers (+ -hearted), bruise."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4937 - συντρίβω - syntríbō - soon-tree'-bo/4937\">G4937</a>, <a href=\"#/G4938 - σύντριμμα - sýntrimma - soon-trim'-mah/4938\">G4938</a>"}]}